flowchart TD
    Start([User lands on /book]) --> Zip[/book/zip<br/>ZIP + Lead Capture/]
    Zip -->|validate-zip OK| ZipForm[Capture name, email, phone]
    ZipForm -->|emit-lead-webhook| Sqft[/book/sqft<br/>Home Size/]
    Sqft --> Offer[/book/offer<br/>Offer Cards/]

    Offer --> OfferA[Tester Deep Clean]
    Offer --> OfferB[Deep + 90-Day Plan<br/>Bundle Reward]
    Offer --> OfferC[Standard Deep Clean]

    OfferA --> Checkout[/book/checkout<br/>Stripe 25% Deposit/]
    OfferB --> Checkout
    OfferC --> Checkout

    Checkout -->|create-payment-intent| Stripe{{Stripe Payment Element}}
    Stripe -->|3DS / confirm| PayResult{Payment OK?}
    PayResult -->|No| Checkout
    PayResult -->|Yes| Race{Confirmation Race}

    Race -->|server-side| Webhook[stripe-webhook<br/>payment_intent.succeeded]
    Race -->|client-side| ClientConfirm[confirm-booking-payment]

    Webhook --> Idempotent{stripe_balance_invoice_id<br/>already set?}
    ClientConfirm --> Idempotent
    Idempotent -->|No| BalanceInvoice[send-balance-invoice<br/>75% remaining]
    Idempotent -->|Yes| SkipInvoice[Skip - already invoiced]

    BalanceInvoice --> Details[/book/details<br/>Address + Schedule/]
    SkipInvoice --> Details

    Details --> Calendar[Closed Calendar Picker<br/>availability_schedule]
    Calendar -->|save-booking-details| SlotCheck{Slot still open?}
    SlotCheck -->|No| Details
    SlotCheck -->|Yes| Webhook2[enhanced-booking-webhook-v2<br/>GHL + Zapier sync]

    Webhook2 --> Confirmation[/book/confirmation<br/>Receipt + Reward/]

    Schedule[/book/schedule<br/>legacy alias/] -.redirect.-> Details
    Confirmation -.guard: missing address?.-> Details

    classDef edge fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0369a1,color:#0c4a6e
    classDef page fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#b45309,color:#78350f
    classDef decision fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#be185d,color:#831843
    class Webhook,ClientConfirm,BalanceInvoice,Webhook2 edge
    class Zip,Sqft,Offer,Checkout,Details,Confirmation,Schedule page
    class PayResult,Race,Idempotent,SlotCheck decision
